subject: Basketball (College)
Draft and Recruitment (Sports)
lead_paragraph: Tyler Ennis, Syracuse’s freshman point guard, said he would enter the 2014 N.B.A. draft. Ennis was second on the Orange in scoring at 12.9 points a game and averaged 5.5 assists.
